snippet.title: Best VGM 588 - Shadow of the Beast - Eerie Forests
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PC Engine (TurboGrafx CD)
Shadow of the Beast (1992)
Eerie Forests
David Whittaker
